    • Constructor Detail

      • CTSAdRequestConfiguration

        public CTSAdRequestConfiguration(java.lang.String serverURL,
                                 java.lang.String playerProfile,
                                 java.lang.String accountId,
                                 java.lang.String contentStreamURL,
                                 IConstants.CTSUrlEncryptionType encryptionTypeForContentStreamURL)
        Create an ad request configuration for CTS integration.
        Parameters:
        serverURL - URL of the CTS server, which should only consist of the protocol and the host, like http://manifest.fwmrm.net
        playerProfile - name of the player profile
        accountId - your CTS account ID provided by CTS
        contentStreamURL - the URL of the original content stream
        encryptionTypeForContentStreamURL - the type of encryption that has been applied to the above URL. It should be either CTS_URL_ENCRYPTION_TYPE_NONE or CTS_URL_ENCRYPTION_TYPE_SHA256.
